"<FF1B>Igor<FF03>Each demon and Persona is classified<FF03>by type!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>There are four main types, such as<FF03>Element and Force!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>!!!As well as sixteen subtypes, such<FF03>as Fire and Death!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>These indicate both the demon's nature<FF03>as well as its strengths and weaknesses!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>For example, Element demons tend to be<FF03>weak to attacks and strong vs! spells!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Contrariwise, Force demons resist<FF03>attacks but tend to be weak to spells!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>In terms of subtypes, Fire demons are<FF03>weak to ice, and resistant to fire!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Taken together, an Element Fire<FF03>demon!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>!!!Would resist fire spells, possibly<FF03>even absorbing them!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But those same fire spells would wreak<FF03>havoc on a Force Water demon!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Do you understand a little better now?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You must grasp your Persona's strengths<FF03>and weaknesses before doing battle!!!<FF02><FF01> Types and subtypes<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas that reach the maximum rank<FF03>of 8 will not grow any further!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>They are powerful in that state!!!<FF03>However!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>If you request that I discard such a<FF03>Persona!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The power of your constant companion<FF03>will be released!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>!!!Leaving behind a tangible memento<FF03>of your time together!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>It may be a weapon, some armor, or<FF03>possibly a gem!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The process is, in fact, the only way<FF03>to obtain certain extremely rare items!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The nature of the items you may attain<FF03>through this process!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>That is for you to discover!<FF02><FF01>Item exchange<FF01><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The Velvet Room is quite spacious!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But even so, there is a limit to how<FF03>many Personas we can look after here!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Sixteen, and no more!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>If you have reached that limit, you<FF03>will be unable to create new Personas!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Remember to clear out unneeded Personas<FF03>in order to make room for new ones!<FF02><FF01>Stocked Personas<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>It pains me to say this, but our methods<FF03>are not as precise as I should like!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Rare though they are, there are times<FF03>when an accident will occur in fusion!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Should this happen, the Persona will<FF03>likely not be the one you aimed for!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>I have no way of predicting the result<FF03>of a fusion accident!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But then, isn't that the way of fate!!!?<FF02><FF01>Fusion accident<FF01><FF1B>Igor<FF03>At times, a newly created Persona will<FF03>inherit skills from its fusion components!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>In this way, you may make Personas with<FF03>skills they would not normally possess!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Do not overlook this principle when you<FF03>seek to create powerful Personas!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The theory behind skill inheritance is,<FF03>alas, somewhat murky!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But we know the spell cards used must<FF03>not have clashing orders!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The type of demon granting the inherited<FF03>skill is also a factor!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Know also that the number of skills a<FF03>Persona can hold is limited!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>And certain special skills cannot be<FF03>passed down!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You should keep this in mind when fusing!<FF02><FF01> Skill inheritance<FF01><FF1B>Igor<FF03>All demons fall into one of several<FF03>categories!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You could classify them by main type,<FF03>subtype, main order, and sub-order!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas lack main and sub-orders, and<FF03>are grouped by order, type, and subtype!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Not only do these indicate their natures,<FF03>they are very important in fusions!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>For example, fusing two of the same type<FF03>tends to result in increased power!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But fusing two opposed types increases<FF03>the risk of fusion accidents!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The same is true for order": 3330,
"Personas hold!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>They are displayed when the Persona-user<FF03>is in certain situations!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>At these times, they will interrupt the<FF03>user to unleash special abilities!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>However, whether this potential is<FF03>displayed all depends on your affinity!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Affinity is indeed quite important!!!<FF02><FF01> Personas' hidden potential<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>There is a sort of affinity between<FF03>humans and Personas!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Not only does this affect whether you<FF03>may take on a Persona!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>It also determines whether or not that<FF03>Persona's potential may be invoked!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>I would recommend choosing Personas<FF03>you have a high affinity with!!!<FF02><FF01>Persona affinity<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>At first, you will be unable to harness<FF03>your Persona's powers to the fullest!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But each time you invoke a Persona,<FF03>its rank will slowly increase!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>In other words, you could say that they<FF03>will grow!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>When that growth reaches a certain level,<FF03>you will have more options in battle!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Even if your Persona learns a powerful<FF03>skill, the SP required remains constant!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Every Persona will grow seven times! If<FF03>it starts at rank 1, it will rise to 8!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas that seem weak at first may<FF03>eventually display surprising strength!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You will grow in combat, but do not<FF03>forget that your Personas grow as well!<FF02><FF01> Persona growth<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas are distinguished by order, too!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You will find that you are incompatible<FF03>with some orders of Persona!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>A Persona's order will affect you,<FF03>particularly in battle!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Take care not to collect too many of<FF03>the same order of Persona!!!<FF02><FF01>Persona orders<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>To take on a Persona is to prepare one<FF03>in this room, to be assumed in battle!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Those Personas you have taken on can be<FF03>actively assumed elsewhere!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>However, you cannot take on Personas<FF03>higher than the user's Persona Level!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas are similar to demons in that<FF03>way!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Push yourself too hard with a low Persona<FF03>level, and your mind can be taken over!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Various assumed Personas grant various<FF03>abilities!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Without the power of Persona, you are<FF03>no different than an ordinary human!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You will be powerless before the arcane<FF03>might of the demons' spells!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>If by chance you were hit by a spell in<FF03>that state, you would be struck down!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>But by taking on a Persona, your defense<FF03>against spells is considerably enhanced!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>For some, it may also confer strength,<FF03>or increase luck for others!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>This, too, is the power of Persona!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Though they are called Personas, each<FF03>is a hidden side of yourself!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>I suggest you examine your status<FF03>carefully after assuming one!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>That way, you can see which of your<FF03>qualities have changed!<FF02><FF01>Taking on Personas<FF01> <FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas are the powers taken from<FF03>demons that will be your strength!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Each of you can take on as many as<FF03>three Personas at once!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Of the three, only one can be actively<FF03>invoked during battle!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>To invoke a Persona is to summon it<FF03>in combat!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>The other two will remain sleeping<FF03>within you on standby!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>Personas on standby are ready to be<FF03>assumed at any time during battle!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Igor<FF03>You could say that understanding your<FF03>Personas' powers is key to survival!!!<FF02><FF01> About Personas<FF01>": 3221,
"<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>What's the matter, <FF07>? Do you<FF03>have business at the historical society?<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Mark<FF03>Heh, then we'll make Kandori fix it!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Mark<FF03>I'll show that guy what happens when you<FF03>mess with St! Hermelin.<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>The Deva System is a terrible thing!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>But!!! was this also part of Kandori's<FF03>scheme?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>Regardless, it's far beyond our capacity<FF03>to fix directly, I'm afraid!<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>It's true. The school's really gone.<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>This must be the Deva System at work!!!<FF03>How dare Kandori unleash such madness.<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>What the--The school's gone. What happened<FF03>to Yuko and everyone.?<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Baffled office worker<FF03>Oh, my God. The east half of town's<FF03>just!!! gone.<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Baffled office worker<FF03>Most of this place seems to be gone<FF03>too, so be careful if you go in there.<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Mark<FF03>Hey, c'mon, man. This ain't the time<FF03>to be wandering around.<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Mark<FF03>Start takin' this seriously. The haunted<FF03>mansion ain't that way!<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>Why are we going back to the school?<FF03>Kandori's in the east side of town!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>!!!You better quit messing around before<FF03>I lose it! Why would we leave town.?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>For heaven's sake!!!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>Why on earth are we leaving town?<FF03>I thought we were going to the hospital!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Mark<FF03>Hey, that's the way out of town!<FF03>Aren't we goin' to the hospital?<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>That girl will be fine! C'mon, we have<FF03>to hurry.<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Mark<FF03>Hey. What're we doin' here? Don't we<FF03>have stuff to do?<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>It's always been here on this side,<FF03>though!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>!!!!!!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Mark<FF03>This place was torn down so they could<FF03>put up the SEBEC building, right?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Mark<FF03>If it's still here!!! does that mean<FF03>we really did go back in time?<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>This used to be a flower garden!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>But ever since it became a forest,<FF03>no one's been able to go inside!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>I thought only you and Maki were allowed<FF03>to enter here!<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Are you going somewhere else? Well, let's<FF03>do that after we meet up with everyone!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Mark<FF03>We don't have a reason to come to this<FF03>dump, right? Then let's go get Kandori!<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>!!!!!!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>Haha!!! Yeah, I'm starting to think so!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>C'mon, let's go.<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Mark<FF03>Maki? What're you talking about? This is<FF03>the hospital you were cooped up in!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Mark<FF03>You have amnesia or somethin'?<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Weird!!! Wasn't this place a castle!!!?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Even before that, I remember it being<FF03>impossible to come here!!!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>What's he so smug for? It's getting<FF03>on my nerves!!! Let's just go!<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>What's he acting all superior about.?<FF03>It really makes me mad.<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>C'mon, guys, let's go. Pbbbbt.<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Man in black<FF03>Past here is SEBEC property. No entry.<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Hey, <FF07>, was the police station<FF03>always a building like this?<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Mark<FF03>Nanjo, you dick!!!<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>I don't recall having anything to do<FF03>at such a shabby place!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>Huh? I thought there was a castle here!!!<FF02><FF01> <FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>Does this look like the police station<FF03>to you? Stop fooling around.<FF02><FF01><FF1B>Nanjo<FF03>Does this look like the police station<FF03>to you? Stop fooling around.<FF02><FF01>": 2886,
"Reiji whistles to himself!<FF01> <FF1B>Reiji<FF03>!!!!!!<FF01><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>I should decide soon which photo I'm<FF03>going to enter in the next contest!!!<FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Hm!!!? Did I remember to turn the lights<FF03>off when I left?<FF01><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Hmm!!! what should I make for dinner!!!?<FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Stay quiet for once and listen to what<FF03>others have to say.<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>And don't you make fun of them, or I'll<FF03>make you regret it.<FF01><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Stop whining. No one likes it.<FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Hey. Didn't they teach you in kindergarten<FF03>not to cause trouble.?<FF01><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>It's better to stay in bed than to go<FF03>through life half-assed!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>There's too many people like that<FF03>already!<FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Y'know, I've been thinking about the<FF03>difference between humans and demons!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>And it's useless! There isn't any!<FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Your actions have no worth unless you<FF03>choose them of your own free will!<FF01> <FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Who the hell do you think you're talking<FF03>to? I hate rudeness worse than anything.<FF01><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Hmph. It's true what they say!!!<FF03>A demon's bark is worse than its bite.<FF01><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>You'll be calling ME a demon soon!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Yukino<FF03>Heheh!!! Now where should I start!!!?<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>I'd watch out if I were you!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>I'm nice and calm now, but I go nuts<FF03>in a snap!<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>I got this hobby!!! I collect severed<FF03>demon heads. Wanna join my collection?<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>You're not gonna do what I say.? Don't<FF03>make me blow your brains out.<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>My daddy was abducted by a UFO!!!<FF03>My mom joined an evil cult!!!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>And now I've been taken apart and put<FF03>back together as a cyborg!!!<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>Won't someone buy my matches!!!? If I<FF03>don't sell any, Papa will beat me!!!<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>I'm the oldest of 23 brothers and<FF03>sisters!!! I have to feed them all!!!<FF01> <FF1B>Ayase<FF03>Ooooh, my chest is sore!!!<FF03>Maybe if you gave it a little rub!!!?<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>C'mon, don't make that awful face!!!<FF03>We just need to get to know each other!<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>Y'know!!! I'm usually really innocent!!!<FF03>But today? I'm feeling daring!<FF01> <FF1B>Ayase<FF03>Hey!!! does it smell funny around here?<FF03>It's you, isn't it? Uchhh, gag me!<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>Wow, you must be REALLY old, 'cause that<FF03>style is like, PRE-prehistoric!<FF01><FF1B>Ayase<FF03>You're seriously willing to be seen<FF03>outside looking like that? What a dork.<FF01> <FF1B>Elly<FF03>I'd like a demon like you to walk me<FF03>home on my way back from school!<FF01><FF1B>Elly<FF03>I have an offer for you! Wouldn't you like<FF03>to protect a beautiful woman like me?<FF01> <FF1B>Elly<FF03>You're a very capable demon! Won't you<FF03>take on a job as my bodyguard?<FF01><FF1B>Elly<FF03>Yes? Would you like some milk?<FF01> <FF1B>Elly<FF03>There!!! that's a dear!!! Goodnight,<FF03>my sweet child!<FF01> <FF1B>Elly<FF03>There, there, little demon!!! Play nice!<FF01>": 2517,
"<FFFC><FF03>!!!Just kidding. Mwahahaha.<FF01> <FF1B>Brown<FF03>Wh!!! What's that.? <FFFC>Hee heeeee.<FF03>You fell for it.<FF01> <FF1B>Brown<FF03>BOO.<FF03>Hehe, did I scare ya?<FF01><FF1B>Brown<FF03>So, got any crushes? Yeah, there's been<FF03>someone on my mind, too!<FF01><FF1B>Brown<FF03>Man, it's hot out. I like summer, but<FF03>not this kind of extreme heat!<FF01><FF1B>Brown<FF03>How've you been? I heard you're on<FF03>a roll! Not me, it's been pretty slow!<FF01> <FF1B>Brown<FF03>Why did the buffalos throw a party on<FF03>their 200th birthday?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Brown<FF03>It was their bisontennial.<FF01><FF1B>Brown<FF03>What do you do if you're on a horse and<FF03>you see a giraffe and lion next to you?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Brown<FF03>Get off the carousel. <FFFC>C'mon, laugh.<FF01><FF1B>Brown<FF03>Alright, what's the difference between<FF03>a rottweiler and a poodle?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Brown<FF03>They're two totally different breeds.<FF03>Get it?<FF01> <FF1B>Brown<FF03>Are you seeing anyone? If you aren't!!!<FF03>How about you and me go out sometime?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Brown<FF03>C'mon, it'll be fun. What do you say?<FF01> <FF1B>Brown<FF03>Hey there. Wanna come to karaoke with me?<FF03>I'm a really good singer!<FF01> <FF1B>Brown<FF03>So you're a demon? So what. C'mon, baby,<FF03>let's play a symphony of love.<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>A-A demon. D-Don't come near me.<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>I got lost and wandered here!!!<FF03>Please forgive me.<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>Eeeeek. Please!!! spare me.<FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Hmm!!! I think your mother's grandpa is<FF03>your guardian angel! He's really strong.<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>Want to know the truth? The ones behind<FF03>all this!!! are really aliens!<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>If you do what I say, by some miracle<FF03>a bronze statue of you will be erected.<FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Hey, how can I get power like yours?<FF03>Because I'm super jealous of it!<FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>Many artists have been captivated by you,<FF03>and now I see why.<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>Are you <FFF3>?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>I could tell right off. You have a unique<FF03>aura about you!!!<FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>I can't do much for you, but I promise<FF03>our time together will be exciting!<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>So c'mon, lend me your strength.<FF01> <FF1B>Maki<FF03>Demons live the way they want, right?<FF02><FF04><FF1B>Maki<FF03>It would be nice if you could put aside<FF03>our differences and help me out!<FF01><FF1B>Maki<FF03>I can only do so much on my own!<FF03>I could use your help!!! Please?<FF01>": 1931,
